description._content: Description: A view in the lagoon of a Gilbert Island atoll. A village communal meeting house can be seen on the left. Location: Gilbert Island, Kiribati ------------------------------------------------------ Description: A typical coral island as seen from an approaching ship. The island of Nanumanga in the Ellice Group. Location: Nanumanga, Kiribati ------------------------------------------------------ Description: A group of children playing the game of "burang-ke", on the beach. Location: Kiribati ------------------------------------------------------ Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/642. This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons. Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown.
